              "html": "<div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:160px 0 80px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.15);position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(196,154,42,0.06) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(196,154,42,0.06) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;pointer-events:none;\"></div><div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;position:relative;z-index:1;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:2rem;\"><a href=\"/\" style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);text-decoration:none;\">Home</a> <span style=\"opacity:.4;\">/</span> <span style=\"color:#C49A2A;\">Careers</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:1.5rem;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:1px;background:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Join the Mission</span></div><h1 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.8rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.04;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 0.4rem;\">Be Part of India's Next</h1><h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.8rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:700;line-height:1.04;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 1.8rem;\"><em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#E2BF68;\">Medtech Revolution</em></h2><p style=\"font-size:1rem;line-height:1.75;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);max-width:640px;margin:0 0 2.5rem;\">At <strong style=\"color:#FFFFFF;\">Bareilly Medtech Incubation &amp; Innovation Labs (BMIIL)</strong>, we're building more than an incubation center \u2014 we're building a movement. A movement that blends <strong style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\">science and innovation</strong>, <strong style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\">Ayurveda and modern medicine</strong>, <strong style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);\">local talent and global vision</strong>.</p><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;\"><a href=\"#openings\" style=\"background:#C49A2A;color:#08122A;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:0.04em;\">View Open Roles</a><a href=\"#apply\" style=\"background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);font-weight:500;font-size:14px;padding:13px 32px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;\">Apply Now</a></div></div></div>"
