            "id": "13e9ux0",
            "elType": "widget",
            "widgetType": "html",
            "settings": {
              "html": "<div style=\"background:#F7F3EC;padding:7rem 0;\"><div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;\"><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:start;\"><div><p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 1.5rem;\">Who We're Looking For</p><h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem);font-weight:300;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 2rem;line-height:1.2;\">People who believe healthcare innovation should reach <em style=\"font-style:italic;\">every corner</em> of India.</h2><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;\"><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.8rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.6rem;flex-shrink:0;\">\ud83c\udf93</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Young Professionals &amp; Graduates</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Eager to learn the ropes of innovation management and make an impact from day one.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.8rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.6rem;flex-shrink:0;\">\ud83d\udd2c</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Researchers &amp; Engineers</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Passionate about medical technology, product development, and clinical problem-solving.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.8rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.6rem;flex-shrink:0;\">\ud83e\udde0</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Mentors &amp; Consultants</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Domain experts who want to contribute their experience to India's growing medtech story.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.8rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.6rem;flex-shrink:0;\">\ud83c\udf0d</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Globally-minded Innovators</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">People who bring local insight and global ambition to demo days, investor pitches, and international exposure.</p></div></div></div></div><div><p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 1.5rem;\">Why BMIIL</p><h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem);font-weight:300;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 2rem;line-height:1.2;\">What you'll gain working here.</h2><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;\"><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.8rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.6rem;flex-shrink:0;\">\ud83c\udfe5</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Hospital &amp; Lab Access</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Work directly inside BIU's teaching hospital, research labs, and clinical infrastructure.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.8rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.6rem;flex-shrink:0;\">\ud83d\ude80</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Ground Floor Opportunity</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Join at the founding stage \u2014 shape the culture, build the systems, define the direction.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.8rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.6rem;flex-shrink:0;\">\ud83d\udcca</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Demo Days &amp; Investor Pitches</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Get exposure to national and international investor events, pitch competitions, and healthcare forums.</p></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.8rem;display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.6rem;flex-shrink:0;\">\ud83c\udfaf</div><div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Real Impact</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Every role directly supports startups solving real healthcare problems for real patients.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
