            "settings": {
              "html": "<div id=\"openings\" style=\"background:#EDE8DE;padding:7rem 0;\"><div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;\"><p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Current Openings</p><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:3rem;\"><h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:300;color:#08122A;margin:0;line-height:1.15;\">We Are Hiring. <strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">Join Us.</strong></h2><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;color:#7A8BA8;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;\">Bareilly, Uttar Pradesh</span></div><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.5rem;margin-bottom:5rem;\"><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem 2.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;width:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.35rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.5rem;line-height:1.2;\">Industry Mentor / Domain Expert</h3><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.2);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;\">Advisory</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;\">&#128205; Remote / Bareilly</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;\">&#9201; Part-time / Consulting</span></div></div><a href=\"#apply\" style=\"background:#C49A2A;color:#08122A;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding:10px 24px;border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;\">Apply Now &#8594;</a></div><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Share your expertise with early-stage medtech startups. Guide founders through clinical validation, regulatory pathways, market strategy, and product development.</p><div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#08122A;background:#EDE8DE;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin:2px 3px 2px 0;\">Domain Expertise</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#08122A;background:#EDE8DE;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin:2px 3px 2px 0;\">Medtech</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#08122A;background:#EDE8DE;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin:2px 3px 2px 0;\">Healthcare</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#08122A;background:#EDE8DE;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin:2px 3px 2px 0;\">Mentorship</span></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem 2.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;bottom:0;width:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;margin-bottom:1rem;\"><div><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.35rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.5rem;line-height:1.2;\">Incubation Manager / Coordinator</h3><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;\"><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.2);padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;\">Core Operations</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;\">&#128205; Bareilly (On-site)</span><span style=\"font-size:12px;color:#7A8BA8;\">&#9201; Full-time</span></div></div><a href=\"#apply\" style=\"background:#C49A2A;color:#08122A;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;padding:10px 24px;border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;white-space:nowrap;flex-shrink:0;\">Apply Now &#8594;</a></div><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#4A5C78;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Lead day-to-day operations of BMIIL's incubation programs \u2014 cohort intake, mentor scheduling, milestone tracking, lab coordination, and startup support across all three tracks.</p><div style=\"display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:4px;\"><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#08122A;background:#EDE8DE;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin:2px 3px 2px 0;\">Program Management</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#08122A;background:#EDE8DE;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin:2px 3px 2px 0;\">Operations</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#08122A;background:#EDE8DE;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin:2px 3px 2px 0;\">Healthcare</span><span style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#08122A;background:#EDE8DE;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:2px;margin:2px 3px 2px 0;\">Team Leadership</span></div></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem 2.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absol